This test checks for Tensor Reduce legal and ilegal partner configurations in erbium.
The following combinations are ilegal:
 - TensorSend/Recv        -> partner_id > 7
 - TensorReduce/Broadcast -> tree_depth > 2

After testing this combinations, the test tries every valid combination for each operation and minion
 - TensorSend/Recv        -> partner_id [0..7]
 - TensorReduce/Broadcast -> tree_depth [0..2]

The test randomize the other arguments using EVL. The argument for
that is that this code would likely run into a regression. Trying to
test every possible combination is too costly, but with randomization,
eventually if should hit every combination.
